race.comment: SHOALWATER BAY (4) went close at Mt Isa and expect that to stack up. Has an inside barrier and the 2kg claim is handy. CASH ARTIST (6) rates similarly on his win at Twin Hills over this trip. He can get some of the money at a p[rice. ICONIC PRINCE (7) was well supported at Emerald but disappointed. His near miss at Rockhampton three back at this level would see him right in the finish. Cormack takes over from Butler. DIASONIC (3) and stablemate MR CALEB (5) aren't badly placed at best. The former will get every chance from the inside barrier and the latter is on a 4-day return with a handy 2kg claim. They can be around the mark.
